		<RichText x="1410" y="255" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">两只岩龙蜥起跳至玩家对侧，造成对应元素的<span color="#f7f978">40%</span><span>伤害，随后均朝玩家翻滚而来，造成对应元素的</span><span color="#f7f978">50%</span><span>伤害。冲刺期间</span><span color="#bfffeb">碰到护盾</span><span>则会眩晕。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#b764b0" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#b764b0">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="739" y="255" width="428" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">两只岩龙蜥起跳至玩家处，造成对应元素的<span color="#f7f978">40%</span><span>伤害，随后朝各自的侧方喷吐蜚火和流霜，持续造成对应元素的</span><span color="#f7f978">40%,<br/>20%,4%,0.4%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="424" height="57" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="HP Simplified Hans" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">熛<span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03">火进行右爪挥扫、左爪拔扯的普通攻击，其依次造成</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" color="#ff9999">40%,50%</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03">伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="703" width="439" height="57" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="HP Simplified Hans" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">熛<span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03">火进行至多3段的震地普通攻击，其依次造成</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" color="#ff9999">50%,50%,75%</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03">伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="927" width="424" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="HP Simplified Hans" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">熛<span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03">火起跳，重重下落，造成</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" color="#ff9999">100%</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03">伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
