		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="479" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">荒寒进行右爪挥扫、左爪拔扯的普通攻击，其依次造成<span color="#99ffff">40%,50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="703" width="439" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">荒寒进行至多3段的震地普通攻击，每段攻击都召唤持续4段的冰棘，造成<span color="#99ffff">30%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="927" width="421" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">荒寒喷出4枚冰锥，冰锥造成<span color="#99ffff">30%</span><span>伤害；冰锥落地形成冰阱，触碰造成</span><span color="#99ffff">70%</span><span>伤害，两种伤害共用(1,0.4,0.1)的衰减。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
