		<RichText x="738" y="1151" width="421" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">当某个龙蜥濒死时，不会立即死亡，另一只龙蜥将在15s后回复其<span color="#ffdfbf">20%/16%/<br/>10%</span><span>的生命值使其重新加入战斗。</span></p>
			</content>
